\mathbb{P}\left(N(t+h)=n+m|\hbox{ }N(t) =n\right) =\begin{cases} 1 - \lambda h + o_0(h) & \text{if }m=0\\ \lambda h + o_1(h) &\text{if } m=1,\\ o_m(h) & \text{if } m>1,\\ \end{cases} 
